body_html: @jungpilyu I am not sure what you are asking. You need to create your own repo with a clone of TensorFlow, make the changes there and submit a pull request here to have the changes committed to the official repo. See https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md
